headline: Morgan Stanley Investment Management Launches Eaton Vance Income Opportunities ETF
summary: NEW YORK, November 10, 2025--Morgan Stanley Investment Management (MSIM) announced today the successful conversion of the Morgan Stanley Income Opportunities Fund into the Eaton Vance Income Opportunities ETF (NYSE Arca: XAGG), expanding its suite of actively-managed fixed income ETFs.
